    "body": "<!-- markdownlint-disable -->\n\n## Purpose\n\nThere have been several linear kernel backends for nvfp4 integrated in vLLM, some added to ModelOpt and some added to compressed-tensors. This PR consolidates all the kernel backends and preparation logic into shared utils that both quant methods can use.\n\n## Test Plan\n\n## Test Result\n\nTested all backends for both checkpoint types, noting that `flashinfer-cudnn` seems broken on main already\n\n### ModelOpt\n\n```\nVLLM_NVFP4_GEMM_BACKEND=flashinfer-cutlass chg run -- vllm serve nvidia/Qwen3-8B-NVFP4 --port 9000\nAccuracy: 0.850\nTotal latency: 8.483 s\nTotal output tokens: 153404\nOutput tokens per second: 18083.703\n\nVLLM_NVFP4_GEMM_BACKEND=flashinfer-cudnn chg run -- vllm serve nvidia/Qwen3-8B-NVFP4 --port 9000\n(EngineCore_DP0 pid=1056963) cudnn._compiled_module.cudnnGraphNotSupportedError: [cudnn_frontend] Error: Deselecting execution plan with name eng0 at position 8\n\nVLLM_NVFP4_GEMM_BACKEND=flashinfer-trtllm chg run -- vllm serve nvidia/Qwen3-8B-NVFP4 --port 9000\nAccuracy: 0.850\nTotal latency: 9.336 s\nTotal output tokens: 153403\nOutput tokens per second: 16431.634\n\nVLLM_NVFP4_GEMM_BACKEND=cutlass chg run -- vllm serve nvidia/Qwen3-8B-NVFP4 --port 9000\nAccuracy: 0.850\nTotal latency: 9.134 s\nTotal output tokens: 153416\nOutput tokens per second: 16795.331\n\nVLLM_NVFP4_GEMM_BACKEND=marlin chg run -- vllm serve nvidia/Qwen3-8B-NVFP4 --port 9000\nAccuracy: 0.861\nTotal latency: 21.340 s\nTotal output tokens: 156557\nOutput tokens per second: 7336.401\n```\n\n### Compressed Tensors\n\n```\nVLLM_NVFP4_GEMM_BACKEND=flashinfer-cutlass chg run -- vllm serve RedHatAI/Qwen3-8B-NVFP4 --port 9000\nAccuracy: 0.854\nTotal latency: 9.131 s\nTotal output tokens: 157000\nOutput tokens per second: 17193.742\n\nVLLM_NVFP4_GEMM_BACKEND=flashinfer-cudnn chg run -- vllm serve RedHatAI/Qwen3-8B-NVFP4 --port 9000\n(EngineCore_DP0 pid=1056963) cudnn._compiled_module.cudnnGraphNotSupportedError: [cudnn_frontend] Error: Deselecting execution plan with name eng0 at position 8\n\nVLLM_NVFP4_GEMM_BACKEND=flashinfer-trtllm chg run -- vllm serve RedHatAI/Qwen3-8B-NVFP4 --port 9000\nAccuracy: 0.854\nTotal latency: 9.683 s\nTotal output tokens: 156993\nOutput tokens per second: 16213.713\n\nVLLM_NVFP4_GEMM_BACKEND=cutlass chg run -- vllm serve RedHatAI/Qwen3-8B-NVFP4 --port 9000\nAccuracy: 0.854\nTotal latency: 9.454 s\nTotal output tokens: 156988\nOutput tokens per second: 16605.468\n\nVLLM_NVFP4_GEMM_BACKEND=marlin chg run -- vllm serve RedHatAI/Qwen3-8B-NVFP4 --port 9000\nAccuracy: 0.877\nTotal latency: 21.427 s\nTotal output tokens: 154053\nOutput tokens per second: 7189.554\n```\n\n---\n<details>\n<summary> Essential Elements of an Effective PR Description Checklist </summary>\n\n- [ ] The purpose of the PR, such as \"Fix some issue (link existing issues this PR will resolve)\".\n- [ ] The test plan, such as providing test command.\n- [ ] The test results, such as pasting the results comparison before and after, or e2e results\n- [ ] (Optional) The necessary documentation update, such as updating `supported_models.md` and `examples` for a new model.\n- [ ] (Optional) Release notes update. If your change is user facing, please update the release notes draft in the [Google Doc](https://docs.google.com/document/d/1YyVqrgX4gHTtrstbq8oWUImOyPCKSGnJ7xtTpmXzlRs/edit?tab=t.0).\n</details>\n\n",
